'''Imoh Umoren''' (wavutse ku ya 13 Kanama 1982), ni umukinnyi wa firime [[Nijeriya|wo]] muri [[Nigeriya]] ukora cyane cyane firime zo mu Buhinde .  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa film ya 2017 ''Abana b'ibyondo'' . Umoren afatwa nkumukinnyi wa mbere wakoze firime wicecekeye wumukara numweru mubikorwa bya firime ya Nollywood. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 13 Kanama 1982 muri [[Nijeriya]]. Se yari umunyapolitiki naho nyina yari umwarimu wa kaminuza.  Umoren avuga ko nyina yagize uruhare mu mwuga we wo gukina filime. Ababyeyi be bombi bapfuye akiri ingimbi, kandi yarezwe na bene wabo kugeza ubwo yikubise wenyine afite imyaka 16. 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka 9, Umoren yatangiye kwandika urukurikirane rusekeje rwitwa ''The Wickeds'' hamwe ninshuti ye magara Richie. Yinjiye nka producer muto muri 'Common Ground Production' kandi akora kumurongo mpuzamahanga witwa ''The Station'' .  Nyuma, yinjiye mubikorwa bya TV bya francise nka ''Project Fame'', ''MTV yo kuburira mbere'', ''Ntuzibagirwe Amagambo'' ''n'imbyino za Street Guinness'' . 

Afite imyaka 26, yakoze filime ye ya mbere yerekana ''Lemon Green''  Filime yamenyekanye cyane. Hanyuma muri 2010, yayoboye film ngufi ''All Sorts Of Trouble'' . Muri 2013, filime ye ya TV Yagize ''Umunsi'' mwiza yatowe nka Cinematografi nziza. Muri 2015 yayoboye firime black and white silent movie ''Hard Times'', imutsindira AMVCA yambere.  Kuri filime ye y’ibyago ''The Happyness Limited'', umukinnyi wa mbere Tope Tedela yatowe nkumukinnyi mwiza muri [[Afurika]] muri Afrika Magic Viewers 'Choice Awards (AMVCA). 

Umoren yaje kwandika no kuyobora film yamamaye cyane''Children of Mud'' ishingiye ku nkuru ifatika.  Filime yakiriye nomination 7 mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime zitandukanye zirimo:[[:en:Nigeria_Entertainment_Awards|Nigeria Entertainment Awards]] (NEA) na AMVCA.  Filime ye y'ibyago yakurikiyeho ''Dear Bayo'' yerekanwe mu birori 11 bya firime kandi yatsindiye ibihembo 6 mu iserukiramuco rya Nollywood mu [[Bwongereza]] andi maserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ya firime.  Umoren yayoboye kandi filime ''Lagos:'' ''Sex, Lies & Traffic'' yafatanije na Gbemisola Afolabi.

Nyuma yarangije gutunganya ikinamico yigihe ''The Herbert Macaulay Affair'', biopic ivuga kuri Herbert Macaulay, muri 2018.   Muri 2020, yakoze urukurikirane rw'ikinamico ''Umuyoboro wa 77'' . 

